m, one day about something he claimed, \u201cO Abu Sa\u2019id, this is not as the jurists say.\u201d Al-Hasan said, \u201cWoe to you! Do you consider only yourself as a jurist? A true jurist is only an ascetic\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13004,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/03\/20\/study-islam-dunya\/","url_meta":{"origin":12707,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Knowledge: Never study Islam for worldly reasons","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 20, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever seeks knowledge that should be sought for the sake of Allah Almighty, but only to gain some worldly benefit, he will never know the fragrance Paradise on the Day of Resurrection.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35053,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/01\/25\/good-dunya-akhirah\/","url_meta":{"origin":12707,"position":3},"title":"Hasan on Dua: Goodness is knowledge in world, Paradise in Hereafter","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 25, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Hisham ibn Hassan reported: Al-Hasan, may Allah have mercy on him, said in regards to His saying, \u201cO Lord, give us good in the world and good in the Hereafter,\u201d (2:201) that good in the world is knowledge and worship, and good in the Hereafter is Paradise. Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33444,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/09\/12\/ask-for-good-dunya-akhirah\/","url_meta":{"origin":12707,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Why not ask for good in this life and the Hereafter?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 12, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, visited a sick man among the Muslims and he was so emaciated that he was like thin bird. The Prophet said to him, \u201cHave you supplicated for anything or asked from Allah?\u201d The man said, \u201cYes. I said:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33118,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/06\/bitterness-dunya-akhirah\/","url_meta":{"origin":12707,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Dunya: Bitterness of world is sweetness in Hereafter","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 6, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe sweetness of the world is bitterness in the Hereafter, and the bitterness of the world is sweetness in the Hereafter.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 22899 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064d